title: Ten Must Have Essential Rap Albums [-emidius-]
description:
The included are considered by many to be some of the top essential Rap albums of all time. In addition they are the top selling Rap albums in history, listed in order. Regardless of any album rankings...these are truly MUST OWN albums for anyone interested in Rap. I hope you enjoy this collection and I will be releasing further collections in the near future.

1. OutKast Speakerboxxx/The Love Below (2003)


2. Eminem The Marshal Mathers LP (2000)


3. The Notorious B.I.G. Life After Death (1997)


4. Eminem The Eminem Show (2002)


5. MC Hammer Please Hammer, Don't Hurt 'Em (1990)


6. 2Pac Greatest Hits (1998)


7. 2Pac All Eyez On Me (1996)


8. Beastie Boys Licensed to Ill (1986)


9. Nelly Country Grammar (2000)


10. 50 Cent Get Rich or Die Tryin' (2003)
